transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Yes.
Executive: Good morning sir, mai Smriti baat kar rahi hu Indiamart se.
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Sir Indiamart.
Customer: Ji boliye.
Executive: Haan ji sir, sir jaanna chahte the sir aapki call aayi thi sir like jaanna chahte the sir kya concern hai aapka?
Customer: Ji madam.
Executive: Sir kal aapki call aayi thi sir, jaanna chahte the kya concern hai sir aapka?
Customer: Ji madam, abhi mai dekhta hu.
